src/sta/doc/OpenSTA.fodt:   <text:p text:style-name="Body_20_first">OpenSTA also supports <text:span text:style-name="T14">statistical timing </text:span>.<text:span text:style-name="T14">anallysis with Liberty Variation Format (LVF) libraries. Statistical timing uses a probaility </text:span>distribution to represent a delay or slew ranther than a single number.</text:p>
