src/sta/doc/OpenSTA.fodt:      <text:p text:style-name="P255"><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font">Subtract the capacitance of all instance pins connected to the net from </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Command_20_Argument">capacitance </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font"><text:span text:style-name="T260">(nets only)</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font">. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font"><text:span text:style-name="T260">If the resulting capacitance is negative, zero is used. </text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font"><text:span text:style-name="T262">Pin capacitance</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font"><text:span text:style-name="T263">s</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font"><text:span text:style-name="T262"> </text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font"><text:span text:style-name="T263">are</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Default_20_Paragraph_20_Font"><text:span text:style-name="T262"> ignored by delay calculation when this option is used.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
src/sta/doc/OpenSTA.fodt:   <text:p text:style-name="P260"><text:span text:style-name="T265">When annotating n</text:span>et wire capacitance <text:span text:style-name="T265">with </text:span>the <text:span text:style-name="Command_20_Argument"><text:span text:style-name="T29">-subtract_pin_load</text:span></text:span> option the capacitance of all instance pins connected to the net is subtracted from <text:span text:style-name="Command_20_Argument">capacitance</text:span>. <text:span text:style-name="T265">Setting the capacitance on a net overrides </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T266">SPEF </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T267">parasitics </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T265">for delay calculation</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T267">.</text:span></text:p>
